theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 16
text = "Required Setup
- Godot Engine 4.x Standard build, recommended Godot 4.3 stable.
- C++ compiler: MinGW/MSYS2 or MSVC on Windows.
- Python 3 plus SCons.
- Git.
- nlohmann/json at src/vendor/json.hpp.
- godot-cpp cloned with the branch matching your Godot version.

Build Settings
- Debug: scons target=template_debug -j4
- Release: scons target=template_release -j4
- Windows explicit: scons platform=windows target=template_debug -j4
- Rebuild every time C++ files change before launching Godot.

Scene Flow
- LoadingScreen.tscn is the intended boot scene.
- TitleScreen.tscn is the main title/menu screen.
- GameWorld.tscn contains Sun, WaveManager, SolarFlare, Towers, Enemies, and HUD.
- PostMortem.tscn handles Sun Extinguished / Victory.

Recommended Workflow
1. Edit src/*.cpp and src/*.h.
2. Run scons target=template_debug -j4.
3. If the native library changed, reload the Godot project.
4. Arrange nodes and exported properties in Godot.
5. Press F5 to run.

Common Fixes
- Entry symbol not found: .gdextension and register_types.cpp must both use perk_the_star_init.
- Failed to load GDExtension: rebuild and match the library path in game/bin/perk_the_star.gdextension.
- gdextension_interface.h missing: run git submodule update --init inside godot-cpp.
- json.hpp missing: place the single-header file at src/vendor/json.hpp.
- Wave JSON issue: validate JSON and confirm res://data/waves/wave_01.json exists.
- Crash on startup: godot-cpp branch probably does not match the Godot version."
autowrap_mode = 3

